---
import Site from '../layouts/Site.astro';
import ShaderHero from '../components/magic/ShaderHero.tsx';
---
<Site title="About & Leadership" description="The Mangalam Coalfield story — a foundation of rich legacy, resilience and shared values, and the leadership carrying it forward at Amlabad, Eastern Jharia.">
  <ShaderHero client:load compact eyebrow="About Mangalam" title="A foundation built to last" accentWords={1} description="Mangalam Coalfield Private Limited is a mine developer and operator reviving the historic Amlabad pits in Eastern Jharia, Jharkhand — built on legacy, run to standard, and committed to responsible coal and cleaner energy." primary={{label:'Our operations', href:'/operations'}} />

  <!-- Our story + Chairman Emeritus tribute -->
  <section class="relative bg-background py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
      <div class="grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[1.2fr_.8fr]">
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04] p-7 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <span class="text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-primary">Our story</span>
          <h2 class="mt-4 font-[var(--font-display)] text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-foreground md:text-5xl">Carrying a vision forward.</h2>
          <div class="mt-6 space-y-4 leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
            <p>Mangalam stands on a foundation of rich legacy, resilience, and shared values — carrying forward the vision of its founder. A new generation now leads, committed to trust, integrity, and excellence in all it builds.</p>
            <p>Today, that commitment is expressed through the revival of the Amlabad block in Eastern Jharia: restoring historic underground coal workings and developing coal bed methane as a cleaner commercial energy stream from the same seams.</p>
            <p>The company operates to the Coal Mines Regulations 2017 and the Mines Act 1952, with qualified statutory officials in every mandated position.</p>
            <p>Our founder's wish was that Amlabad should yield not only coal, but prosperous lives. On what would have been his 60th birth anniversary, in February 2026, his wife — Smt. Urmil Agarwal — inaugurated the <strong class="text-foreground/80">Mangalam Chikitsalaya</strong> at the colliery, a hospital where treatment is free for our workforce and the villages around it. <a href="/cares" class="text-primary underline">See the work we do →</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04] overflow-hidden">
          <div class="relative aspect-[4/5] w-full overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-[#15301f]/50 to-[#0b0e0b]">
            <img src="/images/chairman.jpg" alt="Late Shree Gopal Agarwal, Chairman Emeritus" class="h-full w-full object-cover object-top" onerror="this.style.display='none';this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex'" />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 hidden items-center justify-center p-6 text-center text-[13px] uppercase tracking-wide text-muted-foreground">Portrait of Late Shree Gopal Agarwal</div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-7">
            <div class="font-[var(--font-display)] text-xl font-bold text-foreground">Late Shree Gopal Agarwal</div>
            <div class="mt-2 text-[13px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-primary">Chairman Emeritus</div>
            <p class="mt-4 italic leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">“Through every hardship and setback, Mr. Shree Gopal Agarwal showed that perseverance and unwavering belief in brighter days can transform even the greatest struggles into lasting success. His life reminds us: when we refuse to give up, the future will reward our faith and tireless effort.”</p>
            <p class="mt-3 text-[13px] text-muted-foreground/70">— in memory of Late Mr. Shree Gopal Agarwal, Chairman Emeritus</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Amlabad pits -->
  <section class="relative bg-background pb-6">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
      <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-white/10">
        <img src="/images/amlabad-pits.jpg" alt="The historic Amlabad pit headframes, Eastern Jharia, Jharkhand" class="aspect-[2/1] w-full object-cover" loading="lazy" width="2000" height="1500" />
      </div>
      <p class="mt-3 text-center text-[13px] text-muted-foreground/70">The historic Amlabad pit headframes — Eastern Jharia, Jharkhand.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What guides us -->
  <section class="relative bg-background py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <span class="text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-primary">What guides us</span>
        <h2 class="mt-4 font-[var(--font-display)] text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-foreground md:text-5xl">Trust, integrity, excellence.</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">The values carried forward by a new generation of leadership.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-12 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04] p-7 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary">01</span>
          <h3 class="mt-3 font-[var(--font-display)] text-xl font-bold text-foreground">Trust</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-muted-foreground">Earned through consistency — with our workforce, our partners, and the communities around the mine.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04] p-7 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary">02</span>
          <h3 class="mt-3 font-[var(--font-display)] text-xl font-bold text-foreground">Integrity</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-muted-foreground">Operating to statute and to our word, with safety and compliance treated as the baseline.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04] p-7 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary">03</span>
          <h3 class="mt-3 font-[var(--font-display)] text-xl font-bold text-foreground">Excellence</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-muted-foreground">Engineering rigour and discipline on every shift, underground and above ground.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Leadership -->
  <section class="relative bg-background py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <span class="text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-primary">Leadership</span>
        <h2 class="mt-4 font-[var(--font-display)] text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-foreground md:text-5xl">The team taking it forward.</h2>
        <p class="mt-5 leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">Mangalam is led by a new generation of the founding family, carrying forward the values on which the company was built. Day to day, the colliery is run by qualified statutory officials in every position mandated by the Coal Mines Regulations 2017 — manager, engineers, safety, ventilation and survey — under the oversight of the Directorate General of Mines Safety.</p>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">Individual leadership profiles will be published here shortly.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Site>
